claude-agent-sdk-rs

This crate is an idiomatic Rust port of Anthropic's Claude Agent SDK for Python:

    https://github.com/anthropics/claude-agent-sdk-python

It ports the session reader, the live runtime (the `query()` / streaming client
over the stream-json control protocol, hooks, permission callbacks, and
in-process MCP servers), and local session write ops, along with the SDK's test
suite. The deeper SessionStore-backed integration (store-backed listing,
mirrored resume/import, the transcript-mirror batcher) is not yet ported.

